Zombie_House
By.Prototype 3.1


Quick Tutorial

*Press E above the windows to close them up.
*Break the small boxes on the sides to get more weapons.
*Break the door on top of the ladder to get to roof.
*Press E on the Explosive box to get a HE. (Theres more then one)
*Don't Die!
 
FAQ 

*You can keeping putting blanks into of old ones.
(Making the window stronger) 
*All zombies die when time finishes.
*Only six people can join the human team.(Meant to play with 4) 
*There are two Secrets and you know you have done them when you hear a voice.
*No, the starting voice is not a secret.


Have Fun!


Ill upload the zombie script your meant to use but you can use any script you want.
